---
import { CheckCircle2 } from 'lucide-react';
---
<section class="section-padding bg-anthracite text-text-inverse">
  <div class="container-magsil">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div data-animate data-animate-delay="2">
        <span class="text-gold text-sm font-normal uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Projetos sob medida</span>
        <h2 class="mt-4 mb-6 text-offwhite">Transformamos Referências em Ambientes Únicos</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Atendemos arquitetos, designers de interiores e clientes finais com suporte consultivo completo, do conceito à entrega e instalação.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-muted">
            <CheckCircle2 className="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
            Visita técnica sem custo
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-muted">
            <CheckCircle2 className="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
            Projeto 3D para aprovação
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-muted">
            <CheckCircle2 className="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" />
            Prazo de entrega garantido por contrato
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="/contato"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[52px] px-8 bg-gold text-anthracite text-base font-normal rounded-[var(--radius-md)] hover:bg-gold-light transition-colors duration-base"
          id="projects-cta"
        >
          Falar com Especialista
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="relative" data-animate data-animate-delay="1">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] bg-anthracite-lighter overflow-hidden border border-anthracite-lighter">
          <img src="/images/custom-projects.webp" alt="Projeto sob medida em área gourmet" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="600" />
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative element -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 border-2 border-gold/30 rounded-[var(--radius-lg)]"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
